POS_SRC_MANUAL_OR_UNSPECIFIED

public static final byte POS_SRC_MANUAL_OR_UNSPECIFIED
Constant for identifying a type of position source: manual or unspecified localization. In this case the client application injects an external location by invoking #setManualWGS84Position(double, double, float).
